  <brief_title>Treatment of Whiplash Associated Disorders by APOS Kit</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial Which Compare the Effectiveness of an APOS Kit With Short Waves Therapy for Treating Whiplash Associated Disorders</official_title>
